metadata.name: Anatomy of a Death-Head Moth
metadata.description:
Death head moth is a symbol of death. Or is it?  people refer to these unique beings as the “night creatures” because of the dead head moth’s deadly feature. Some say it has dark and negative vibes, which could also lead to bad luck for many or it portrays a person who has deep and dark thoughts. Some see it as being of manipulation and trickiness, as moths are one of the few creatures who are easily destroyed by bees. So, to save themselves, they have to use their tricks. 

Often the death head moth is associated with dreams. Interestingly, many people believe that if you see one in your dream, especially one that goes towards a light source, it means there is something you want in life. However, you’re too scared to share it with anyone. Sometimes these dreams can also help you find the answers to your questions.

How will you see the anatomy of a dead head moth NFT and how will you use its energy?
